{"tid":619402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係元朗合益街市執到個銀包","createTime":"2018-04-06T15:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T17:14:53.000Z","uid":3344,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ce491f3dc333889a23955e769d2980782e7facbf","tid":619402,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/230411_e5e5842e5b377c7bdb44b33c611c3b6c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F230411_e5e5842e5b377c7bdb44b33c611c3b6c.png&h=d25f4610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日我媽咪係元朗合益街市執到個銀包<br />\n時間大約係兩點幾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇過入面都有幾多證件 希望銀包可以搵得番主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果個銀包真係你既 話比我聽你身份證號碼係咩 同埋叫咩名 同你確認番身分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hereweare2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhereweare2&d=OJlPO1j1NBv%2FxoQriCu%2BAkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=e3ba41a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hereweare2</a>"},{"pid":"fd4586c80447c58b31d9c988a19ea72d81c43282","tid":619402,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91846e14116e1f8021d911d0ec81d6344c07b56e","tid":619402,"uid":1255,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"拎去比警犬好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都識上連登 唔識去警局?"},{"pid":"087aaac59598cc153f97d913795278d2d29c12f2","tid":619402,"uid":139055,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"有好多證件就直接拎去差館啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"fe6fd595b6dc18c488179563bdb45c1e4ad615a7","tid":619402,"uid":3344,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果聽日下午五點前都無人認領 我會拎去差館</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"272efa580b1def1b5942c68bb48d1c14e86520b8","tid":619402,"uid":58374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:12:57.000Z","msg":"拾遺不報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524ea805ee38d02a7977a186daf98118a2a60b1f","tid":619402,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:16:14.000Z","msg":"可能人地報左警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你諗住幾時比返人地同個官講啦"},{"pid":"09b0c99ae041302466ec3e103a773263be2bc02a","tid":619402,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:18:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7be3c0cfae03fec11fba552b0b397de79ad4bcb7","tid":619402,"uid":24675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:20:45.000Z","msg":"有心就交去差館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n信樓主真心幫人而唔係搏有車馬費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3161e05000140dd79b08af4687e03b7de326108","tid":619402,"uid":136760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:21:01.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接送去差館，然後再開po通知佢叫佢自己去拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？可能你冇咩居心，不過真係多舊魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc36985ec5e502d4655a125bcda5e66f0d671f88","tid":619402,"uid":137997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:26:59.000Z","msg":"你而家唔拎落差館你就有排煩 你聽朝慢慢同差佬解釋啦"},{"pid":"ef07bad95908416fa2163adde8c3a0fec4c668ed","tid":619402,"uid":32721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:27:09.000Z","msg":"俾返人啦"},{"pid":"b8859e628e5261ac66ed778adebeceb18ef80b69","tid":619402,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:37:37.000Z","msg":"一係就掉撚左佢 一係而家就找去差館<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愈遲就愈麻煩"},{"pid":"44ed467253536c6c80f1d214e17a81359cfc77ea","tid":619402,"uid":56954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"09b0c99ae041302466ec3e103a773263be2bc02a","tid":619402,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:18:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:44:15.000Z","msg":"唔比樓主執到野既地方或者路過既地位離差館好遠所以唔拎去住既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果我係樓主,比失主咁屌法我以後執到野一定唔比返人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9153dd77f784203127df23f15aeb271bddc924f1","tid":619402,"uid":3344,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T16:06:00.000Z","msg":"補充返,<br />\n我係樓主既男朋友.<br />\n個銀包係佢媽咪今日係街市執到, 佢媽咪本身係諗住成個銀包都唔俾返人.<br />\n佢今晚拎左返黎,我女朋友勸左佢媽咪好耐,佢先決定交返出去.<br />\n而離佢屋企最近既警署都有一段距離,<br />\n佢係打算聽日出街就拎埋出去報失,<br />\n我覺得佢而家呢個決定已經係最好既做法,<br />\n如果我女朋友係因為無即時係屋企拎個銀包去差館, <br />\n而令到我佢犯法既話,<br />\n我諗只會有愈黎愈多既香港人係拾為不報<br />\n到時候你班連登仔唔好上黎開post話問有無巴絲打係車執到咩電話銀包,<br />\n自己去差館等認領啦"},{"pid":"8fffc7141200c5a793cc6ceaf1ab771751101eb8","tid":619402,"uid":68081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9153dd77f784203127df23f15aeb271bddc924f1","tid":619402,"uid":3344,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T16:06:00.000Z","msg":"補充返,<br />\n我係樓主既男朋友.<br />\n個銀包係佢媽咪今日係街市執到, 佢媽咪本身係諗住成個銀包都唔俾返人.<br />\n佢今晚拎左返黎,我女朋友勸左佢媽咪好耐,佢先決定交返出去.<br />\n而離佢屋企最近既警署都有一段距離,<br />\n佢係打算聽日出街就拎埋出去報失,<br />\n我覺得佢而家呢個決定已經係最好既做法,<br />\n如果我女朋友係因為無即時係屋企拎個銀包去差館, <br />\n而令到我佢犯法既話,<br />\n我諗只會有愈黎愈多既香港人係拾為不報<br />\n到時候你班連登仔唔好上黎開post話問有無巴絲打係車執到咩電話銀包,<br />\n自己去差館等認領啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T16:26:11.000Z","msg":"似水兄好波，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打一大段野把曲變成直<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbc8e53ae85125b5e0c5240b0671fd00b5bed5b","tid":619402,"uid":68081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"本來我想講事實，不過算了，事不關己，我先唔會多事，似水兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果不是多事我同佢都唔會認識，大家晚安。"},{"pid":"1128494af8d7b9b2ad0c543498d5fa81912fd74b","tid":619402,"uid":165067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:14:53.000Z","msg":"傻閪拎去差館啦 全世界上連登咩"}]}